title: Denver Nuggets Predictions and Observations With Adam Mares | Weekends with Wos
description:
Wos is back from hiatus and is joined by Adam Mares, VP of creative production at DNVR Sports and host of two Nuggets podcasts, to discuss their thoughts, predictions and all-around observations about this year's Denver Nuggets team.
Host: Wosyn Lambre
Guest: Adam Mares
Producer: Jade Whaley
